      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Since 0.14, the dbcache will borrow unused memory space from the mempool, so it can grow to 1.3 GB in your case (assuming you didn't increase the mempool). Also, bitcoind can use a few hundred MB of RAM in addition to the mempool and dbcache.\r\n\r\nHow do you observe that it grows beyond 1000mb?",
